EN: People lead a relatively comfortable life in this peripheral city.

ZH: 这个地方位于人类的文明边沿。
EN: This place is located on the fringes of human civilization.

ZH: 他居住在这个国家的政治边沿地带。
EN: He lives in the political periphery of this country.

