EN: This road winds along the edge of the mountain range.

ZH: 这个城市坐落在大河的边沿地带。
EN: This city is situated in the peripheral area of a big river.

ZH: 它们生长在沙漠边沿的绿洲地区。
EN: They grow in the oasis areas on the fringes of the desert.

ZH: 在附近的边沿地带，你可以采集到很多野花。
EN: You can collect a lot of wildflowers in the nearby fringe areas.

ZH: 这个地区的边沿山峰非常险峻。
EN: The fringe peaks in this region are very steep.

ZH: 这里的边沿地带荒芜而人迹罕至。
EN: The fringe areas here are desolate and rarely visited.

ZH: 这座城市建在森林边沿的山丘上。
EN: This city is built on the hills at the edge of the forest.

